product.name: Right Headlight for Hyundai Elantra 2017 2018, Right Passenger Side Front Halogen Headlight Assembly 114-10015R,92102F3000, HY2503206 (Right/Passenger Side)
product.description: Specification Housing Color:Black Placement on Vehicle:Front, Right Interchange Part Number: 114-10015R,92102F3000, HY2503206 Assembly Type:Composite Fitment Type:Direct Replacement Bulb Type: Halogen Headlight Style:Factory Lens Color: Clear Fit (As a Reference) Headlights for Hyundai Elantra 2017 2018 4-Door Sedan NOT Compatible with Factory LED Headlight Models NOT Compatible with Factory LED Daytime Running Lamp Models ONLY Compatible with Factory Halogen Headlight Models Package Includes 1 x Right Headlight (Passenger Side) NOTE: Please check carefully whether it is consistent with our plug before buying.
product.bullet_points:
• 【Fitment】This right headlight for Hyundai Elantra 2017 2018; OE/OEM part number:114-10015R,92102F3000, HY2503206 (Right/Passenger Side)
• 【Easy to Install】The right headlight is made with original specifications and original style, crystal clear lens matches the matte black housing. Plug & Play. Simply plug the factory wiring harness into the new lights, simple, quick and easy to complete the installation
• 【Attention】 This headlight for Hyundai Elantra 2017 2018 is only compatible with factory halogen headlight models; not compatible with factory LED headlight models and factory LED daytime running light models
• 【Good Light Transmission】The lampshade of this halogen headlight is made of high-quality material with high light transmission and eye-catching. Even when driving in bad weather such as heavy rain, fog or snow, it can still be a good reminder to the vehicles or pedestrians behind you
• 【High Quality Material】The right head light is made of sturdy and durable PC and PP material, which has good heat dissipation, abrasion resistance, strong impact resistance and not easy to scratch. Its superior sealing makes the tail light has excellent waterproof and dustproof effect, long service life
